Title: Covariant - tensor method for quantum groups and applications I

$SU(2)_{q}$Comments: 18 pages

Journal-ref: J.Phys. A26 (1993) 4595-4606

A covariant - tensor method for $SU(2)_{q}$ is described. This tensor methodis used to calculate q - deformed Clebsch - Gordan coefficients. The connectionwith covariant oscillators and irreducible tensor operators is established.This approach can be extended to other quantum groups.